# Docs And Repo Metadata Workflow

- Small maintenance in docs, Cursor rules, Cursor skills, and `.github` metadata may stay on `main` if the user wants the hybrid fast path.
- If the change expands beyond small maintenance, switch back to the default branch-first workflow.
- Even for metadata changes, do not commit or push unless the user explicitly asks.
- Keep documentation, PR templates, and Cursor guidance consistent with `docs/github_workflow.md`.
